column1: ait_39. What is your trust level to utilize Artificial Intelligence or Fully Autonomous Technologies?
column2: ait_40. What is your trust level to utilize a Self-Driving car when this technology becomes available?
column3: ait_41. What is your trust level that self-driving cars will keep your own safety as it's primary objective?
column4: ait_42. What is your trust level that self-driving cars will be able to navigate in construction zones that include temporary detours that would ordinarily go against the flow of traffic?
column5: ait_43. What is your trust level that self-driving cars will be able to navigate in crowded pedestrian areas?
column6: ait_44. What is your trust level that self-driving cars will successfully get you to the EXACT destination you requested?
column7: ait_45. What is your trust level in the ability of self-driving cars to navigate safely with no-person in the vehicle.
